    The ingest plugin does the work of translating a URL to a set of SimpleFeatures that can be ingested into GeoWave. While the ingest system offers options for Avro serialization and ingest from HDFS, the MinimalSimpleFeatureIngestPlugin is the simplest way to create a plugin that ingests data that uses a custom format from the local file system. For examples of more complex ingest plugins, including ones that support Avro serialization and mapreduce ingest, see the formats that are built in to GeoWave.
